    <item>
      <title>法院允许债务清偿，Byju’s 避免破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/byju-s-averts-bankruptcy-as-court-allows-settlement-on-debt-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Byju’s 获得了偿还印度板球管理委员会所欠 1900 万美元的时间，此举使这家在线辅导初创公司暂时避免了破产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/byju-s-averts-bankruptcy-as-court-allows-settlement-on-debt-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 11:04:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃克森美孚业绩超出预期，先锋交易推动创纪录产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/exxon-surpasses-expectations-as-pioneer-deal-fuels-record-output</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚公司以 630 亿美元收购先锋自然资源公司后，石油和天然气产量创下历史新高，利润超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/exxon-surpasses-expectations-as-pioneer-deal-fuels-record-output</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:30:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙因规则警告退出加州，转投德州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/chevron-misses-earnings-estimates-adding-to-hess-delay-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙公司 (Chevron Corp.) 正在将总部从加利福尼亚迁至休斯顿，此前该公司曾多次警告称，加州的监管制度使美国成为难以开展业务的地方。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/chevron-misses-earnings-estimates-adding-to-hess-delay-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:16:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚债务流程重新调整 49 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/ethiopia-expects-debt-process-to-reprofile-4-9-billion-of-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚计划和财政部长菲特苏姆·阿塞法表示，埃塞俄比亚预计其债权人将同意重组 49 亿美元的债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/ethiopia-expects-debt-process-to-reprofile-4-9-billion-of-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 08:26:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴菲特继续抛售美国银行，抹去其对美国同行的领先地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/warren-buffett-dumps-bofa-s-stock-for-12th-straight-trading-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃伦·巴菲特连续第 12 天抛售美国银行公司的股票，抹去了该银行今年在基准指数中的领先地位，因为他的企业集团削减了长期投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/warren-buffett-dumps-bofa-s-stock-for-12th-straight-trading-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 02:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克 100 指数因就业数据从高点跌至 10%：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[疲软的就业报告引发了人们对美联储降息速度过慢、可能导致经济放缓加剧的担忧，导致股市抛售加剧，债券收益率暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
